{"tid":1108330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(環保撚) 調查揭港人日耗 6500萬張紙巾 2900萬張抹手紙 980萬張濕紙巾","createTime":"2019-04-16T01:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T02:16:07.000Z","uid":56881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"98d618e447909b54476339b80701500ba51eb78b","tid":1108330,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8F%AD%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%A5%E8%80%97-6500%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE-2900%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E6%8A%B9%E6%89%8B%E7%B4%99-980%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E6%BF%95%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE-214500944.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2580%2597-6500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B7%25BE-2900%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%258A%25B9%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25B4%2599-980%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%25BF%2595%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B7%25BE-214500944.html&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=61b5c813\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8F%AD%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%A5%E8%80%97-6500%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE-2900%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E6%8A%B9%E6%89%8B%E7%B4%99-980%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E6%BF%95%E7%B4%99%E5%B7%BE-214500944.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有環保團體進行的調查發現，港人使用紙巾量驚人，每日使用逾六千五百萬張紙巾，二千九百萬張抹手紙及九百八十萬張濕紙巾！該團體將於七月十五日舉行惜「紙」一天行動，呼籲市民及商戶減少用紙，預計有約三百至四百間商戶參加。<br />\n<br />\n對紙類回收認知不足<br />\n<br />\n世界綠色組織訪問五百名港人，發現近六成人每日外用膳時使用二至四張紙巾，近一成人使用八至十張，百分之六人更使用超過十一張，推算港人外出用膳日耗三千四百七十萬張紙巾；即使在家用膳，港人亦毫不「慳紙」，紙巾消耗量達三千零四十萬張，總計平均每人每日用八點七張，日用十五張以上的人更有百分三，較在外用膳更高。<br />\n<br />\n另外，近五成人每日使用兩至四張抹手紙，兩成人每日用五至七張，推算港人每日使用兩千九百萬張抹手紙。濕紙巾則有兩成人每日用兩至四張，一成六人用一張，估計每日消耗量為九百八十萬張。<br />\n<br />\n組織行政總裁余遠騁指，該兩種紙因成分問題而無法回收，但調查中只有三成二人知道抹手紙不能回收，反映市民對紙類回收認知不足。他指現時年輕人習慣使用紙巾，因此應由教育做起，鼓勵學生以手巾代紙巾，又指在家亦可以毛巾代替紙巾抹餐具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遲D連紙巾都唔比用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a82fbb847917bbffab0a165122aa6079d0c61e","tid":1108330,"uid":159990,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"香港咁又人鼻敏感 點用手巾"},{"pid":"b0979a6c81fbdaf97e3a1ac602b2824c40c780c0","tid":1108330,"uid":247923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"打飛機用手巾?"},{"pid":"d343a1c11bb9cde6007c8a01a0c8399ec9d8e0ea","tid":1108330,"uid":54777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"港人日打2900萬次飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07db69714aad102a32bd29672a6b6bd5fa80fd66","tid":1108330,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"on9 空氣汙濁呀 <br />\n消滅左支那 還我清新空氣咪唔用紙巾囉"},{"pid":"0bdc9bb4e0faa9216d03ad94d3d52a587094fc25","tid":1108330,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"我好撚環保架,<br />\n一張紙巾用成日,<br />\n抹鼻涕, 抹嘴都係用同一張,<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c279d893a29ecc1c8c8c34e62104f6f069d9cec","tid":1108330,"uid":224510,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqYJDoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqYJDoh.jpg&h=251d62bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0c86f7787d32a0c424e84d2ffe0824a7b7089e","tid":1108330,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:41:08.000Z","msg":"咁少咋<br />\n等我用多啲先"},{"pid":"ca4ce3dcf25458f0f6b1801f7445fa1960f19f91","tid":1108330,"uid":34773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"人就